705090f-a.text:
(1)
494 Jamaica Ave., south side, between Linwood and Elton Streets, showing the William Stoothoff farmhouse, which was owned by Frank E. Hart in 1889, B. Benzinger in 1923 and also occupied by Theo. Van Wyck at one time.
April 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(2)
The same, showing a side view.
Aptil 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
